survey_response.review_text: She is a skilled doctor and can treat kids with care. So far we are completely satisfied with her treatment.

We have a 5 year old daughter with 4 bad teeth and she required immediate RCT. All the dentists in Kolkata said a GA is required to do the root canal successfully as she is not very cooperative. We definitely did not want to go for a GA on a 5 year old child. Dr Pooja Singh was amazing with my daughter and she successfully did 3 RCT's on her. Dr Singh was so gentle and caring with my daughter, that she caused no problems during the RCT process. We don't have words good enough to thank the doctor.  Thank you doctor. We are very grateful to you.

I took my son to Apurva Dental Care for dental issues several times. I am very pleased with their service and friendly staff. Dr. Puja Singh is exceptionally good with kids, so much that my son does not fear to visit this clinincs. We visited twice during covid time and found this place well equipped with covid norms and following them, which is also very nice.

*** ** * **** **** ****** *** very serious ,honest to her profession , very well behaved with professanalism ,deal with kids very nice , fees is moderate according to her efficiency , location of her chamber is very good at garihat but should be more promininent , with glow sign board

We observed doctor Pooja Singh very intelligent and able to segregate possible cause of the decay in my son's teeth (who is just 3.5 yrs of age). Her experience and analysis of the problem was very helpful to us...now we are feeling very positive that my kid's teeth will be prevented from further decay *** **** *** ***** *** ***** Thanks to the doctor for her ******* *********, polite nature and expert in handling the kid's fear for treatment.

Dr. Pooja is a saviour for mother like me.
